description: This updated 1,211 sq. ft. corner-unit condo offers 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, combining modern style with everyday convenience. The open-concept kitchen features a spacious island, stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, and a gas oven—ideal for cooking and entertaining. Renovated with contemporary finishes, the primary suite boasts a double vanity and a soaking tub for a spa-like retreat. Natural light fills the living area, highlighted by a working fireplace, recessed lighting, and hardwood floors. Dual Pane Windows enhance comfort, while custom and California closets provide ample storage. A private covered rear deck offers outdoor space for relaxation. Additional perks include central air, gas heat, an in-unit washer and dryer, one assigned parking space, private storage, an intercom system, and elevator access. Offer deadline of Monday, March 29, at 5:00 PM. Please make offers good until 10:00 AM Tuesday.
